It is believed to have been located in {{ill|Kanzaki District, Hizen Province|ja|神埼郡|12=draft|12=draft}}, corresponding to present-day {{ill|Kanzaki, Saga|ja|神埼市|12=draft|12=draft}} in {{ill|Saga Prefecture|ja|佐賀県|12=draft|12=draft}}.

=== Size ===
As of {{ill|Shōō (era)|ja|正応|12=draft|12=draft}} 5 (1291), it covered approximately 3,000 chō.

